attributedString.string:
Reconfigured the layout of the Components page. The components are no longer all on one artboard but split into five boards: Controls, Inputs, Content, Navigation, Informative, and Data Tables.
		Removed the Add-ons page from the Kit, however all the Add-on symbols still live in the Kit library.
		Updated input visual style and interaction, including new input field background color field-02. Affects the following components
		Text Input
		Text Area
		Dropdown
		Select
		Date & Time Picker
		Search
		Slider Number input
		Several color changes have been made to make colors more accessible. This included changing hex values and roles for some of the colors. The new updated pallete is available with this sketch download from GitHub. The changes include (bold indicates a new color token):
		$ui-05 > #5A6872 (passing 4.5:1, high contrast border, secondary icons)
		$ui-04 > #8897A2 (passing 3:1, now used for emphasis borders)
		$ui-03 > #DFE3E6 (not passing 3:1, now used for subtle borders)
		$support-01 > #E0182D (passing 4.5:1)
		$text-03 > #CDD1D4 (not passing 4,5:1, used only for placeholder text)
		$field-01 > #F4F7FB  (input field background on ui-01)
		$field-02 > #FFFFFF (input field background on ui-02)
		$inverse-02 > #272d33 (passing 4,5:1)
		Hover colors have been updated and added and now have corresponding class names. These swatches have been added to the Carbon Default Palette (plugin). The colors include:
		$hover-danger  #bd1427
		$hover-primary  #30588c
		$hover-primary-text  #294c86
		$hover-row  #5596e6 @ 10% opacity
		$hover-secondary  #3d70b2
		Tooltip
		Updated the visual and interaction of the original Tooltip
		No longer known as Tooltip but Interactive Tooltip
		It now opens on click not hover
		Can include a button and/or link within Interactive Tooltip as needed 
		Code Snippets
		Updated Code and Terminal Snippet visual and interaction styles.
		Made snippets lighter (color changes)
		Added in variation with line numbers
		Can only scroll horizontally
		Code snippet has a set height on default state, has a varying height based on content in expanded state
		Added symbols to all artboards in the Layout Templates pages
		Made components on the library more flexible and customizable
		Icons
		Decreased icon size from 24x24px to 16x16px
		All glyphs have been deprecated. A few of the old glyph solid styles exist in the new icon library and are represented by the `- -solid` ending
		For more details on icon changes: https://github.com/carbon-design-system/carbon-icons/blob/master/docs/migration-guides/migration-v7.md
		Added in links to the Library Section on the Getting Started page to tutorials and wiki with more information on how to use Libraries
